
He walks up to me and places his finger under my chin, making me look up at him. "I'm sorry that I got mad at you... I just want you near me, when you said that you could take any other room, I got angry. Your mine Rosaline!" He said soothingly, but with a stern voice as well.
"Its okay..." I whisper. He places a kiss on my forehead."I have to go take care of some last minute Alpha duties, so make yourself at home, don't leave!" He says. I nod. He leaves the room and a door slam. I sigh and flop down on the bed.What have I gotten myself into?
